@POLES APART
$
REMEMBER:

1. Yoy _can_ save at any time during the
level, not just at the end.

2. I do not recommend shooting off more
than 1 bullet at a time, as Frostbite will
not register it. Also, don't shoot
directly at a wall, as he WILL register it
and a spear will be wasted.

3. Walruses require shooting 3 times, and
they can destroy you with one hit.

4. Kill all the enemies before you can
progress to the next level.

         That's all! Enjoy!
$

    end
